Dah Sing buys HK $ 578 . 8 mln office floors . Dah Sing Financial Holdings Ltd ' s wholly owned banking unit Dah Sing Bank Ltd has agreed to buy offices in North Point on Hong Kong island from a third party for HK $ 578 . 83 million cash , Dah Sing said on Friday . The property comprises four floors , covering a total gross floor area of about 83 , 888 square feet , in Island Place Tower in North Point . The construction of the grade A office building is expected to be completed in mid - 1997 , it said . Dah Sing Financial said the purchase would reduce operating expenses in the long run by saving on office rental costs . - - Hong Kong Newsroom ( 852 ) 2843 6370 
